Steps to Reproduce:
1. Add this
   {
     "files.trimTrailingWhitespace": true
   } 
   in your user settings file
2. Type
   function hi(){

   var ldsfjsdlf;
   }
   Actual :Not Clearing empty lines when i press enter/any trigger
   Excepeted:Should clear empty lines 

Proof:
![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/12810078/15897827/9f976720-2db3-11e6-803a-3320a7569c32.png)

- VSCode Version: 1.2.0
- OS Version: OS X 10.11.5 (15F34)

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create empty file with such content: 
   `code {
   some code {
      another code {
      }
   }
   }
   `
2. Save your file, and place cursor just after last opening bracket.
3. Press 'return' to make newline and press cmd+s to save your file. 
4. Notice, how cursor is jumping to the beginning of the new line ignoring indentation

gif: ![output](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/103639/15895846/1721cde4-2d96-11e6-9981-d22c8b7d6b9a.gif)

